  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Contract<br /><strong>Duration:</strong> 3 Months ( chance to be converted )<br /><strong>Salary Range:</strong> Up to SGD 2,400 per month<br /><strong>Work Location:</strong> Greenwich / Serangoon North<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li><p>5-day work week</p></li><li><p>8:00 AM to 5:45 PM</p></li></ul><h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are seeking Temporary Warehouse Crew to support daily warehouse and logistics operations. The successful candidates will be responsible for handling inventory, packing activities, and ensuring warehouse processes are carried out safely and efficiently.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Update and maintain accurate stock records in the system</p></li><li><p>Assist with stock counting and inventory checks</p></li><li><p>Perform picking and packing of goods according to requirements</p></li><li><p>Comply with warehouse SOPs and safety guidelines</p></li><li><p>Support general warehouse and logistics operations as required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Prior warehouse experience is preferred</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to lift and move goods when required</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to commit for the full 3-month contract period or longer</p></li><li><p>Possession of a forklift license will be an added advantage</p></li></ul>",
